The President of the United States of America has mocked Iran in an interview on FOX TV for there inability to identify a passenger plane from a war plane. He speak You are weaker than we thought Iran since you cannot identify a passenger plane from a war plane you are more weak, You want to fight America we will come like a ghost in the night before you wake up in the morning Iran is doomed, we only took out a terrorist who has killed thousands of people and he is planning to kill more you are complaining. He added people dont understand what i have done to the world by Taking Soleimani out even Iranians are Ignorant of that..